source.name: Veterans Health Administration 2010 Facility Quality and Safety Report - Population Quality of Care
source.description: Composite scores reflecting quality of care for outpatients (NEXUS) and inpatients (ORYX). Quality of outpatient care is further stratified by comparison of outpatient care by gender and age.
